high_descs: Turn right then face the counter to your left.
Take the knife off of the counter in front of you.
Turn left and face the stove in front of you.
Slice the lettuce by the stove in front of you.
Turn around and face the cabinet to your left.
Place the knife inside and close the cabinet.
Turn left and face the stove in front of you.
Take a lettuce slice off of the counter in front of you.
Turn around and face the sink on your left.
Wash the lettuce in the sink and take it out.
Turn right and face the green bin on your left.
Place the lettuce in the green bin in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place clean lettuce in the green bin.

high_descs: Turn to the right, go across the room and turn to the right.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn right and go across the room.
Cut the lettuce on the counter.
Turn to the right and then turn complete around.
Put the knife in the cabinet below the counter.
Turn left towards the counter.
Pick up a slice of lettuce on the counter.
Turn around and head to the sink.
Put the slice of lettuce in the sink, rinse it and pick it back up.
Turn right, go across the room and turn left.
Put the slice of lettuce in the recycling bin.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean slice of lettuce in the recycling bin.

high_descs: Turn right and cross the room and then turn left to face the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn left and cross the room to face the counter.
Cut the lettuce on the counter into slices.
Turn right and look down to face the left most cabinet.
Place the knife in the cabinet all the way to the left under the counter.
Turn left and step forward to face the counter.
Pick up the slice of lettuce on the counter.
Turn to the right and step forward to face the sink.
Wash the slice of lettuce in the sink and then remove it.
Turn right and walk across the room and turn left to face the trash can.
Place the slice of lettuce in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: To clean a slice of lettuce and place it in the trash can.
